<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Westminster" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Westminster,</orth> the western part of London; seat of the royal palace: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.384" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 384</bibl>. <cit><quote>abbot of W.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.152" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 152</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.6.19" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 6, 19</bibl>. The kings crowned in the cathedral: <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.37" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.4.31" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 32</bibl>.
